descript.abstract: To provide the county with up to date political boundaries at the local level. Area polygons are identified with the Precinct Name, Number and the designated commissioner, legislative, congressional area number. Last updated on 27 APRIL 2017 by KLB.
descript.purpose: Thurston County voting precinct boundaries; congressional districts; commissioner districts; and legislative district information is given in this layer.

timeperd.current: Layer gets updated as boundaries change.
